reviewText: I Saw Bobby Collins back when he used to host VH-1 Spotlight & The Improv so when i came across this DVD I had to grab it-Was Great..I would recommend this DVD to anyone who watched Night at the Improv or VH-1 Spotlight or to anyone who enjoys Stand-Up!
Title: Bobby Collins Live!

reviewText: Bobby Collins used to be the #1 comic in America to me a few years ago. However, with the last 2 DVD's and last 2 cd's, all with duplicate material, it is a shame that I can no longer say that.  he is still one of my favorites but this DVD has the same old material he was doing years ago.  I'd love to see a new and improved up to date Bobby.
Title: Bobby Collins Live!

reviewText: This DVD is hilarious from start to finish.  Bobby Collins is a riot. Too bad there aren't any other DVDs of his available.
summary: One of the best comedy DVDs ever
Title: Bobby Collins Live!

reviewText: I have always likes his standup. It's not heavy on the vulgarity and really gets his audience laughing. Wish I could see him in person.
Title: Bobby Collins Live!

reviewText: I had never heard of Bobby Collins, then I started hearing him on the comedy channel on sirius radio.  He is very funny.  I really enjoyed the dvd.
Title: Bobby Collins Live!
